00:08:32.090 --> 00:08:34.090
Algunas cosas le temen al fuego.

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.490
pero no de luz.

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:54.210
Chang Dong.

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:44.280
¡Corre, papas fritas!

00:09:47.250 --> 00:09:47.800
